From faa8242d2580886b97fd9e9528ae6f9442dc80e6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:06:06 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ADD selected-agent backend command routing to keep slash
 commands out of prompt sends

Selected agent messages that are slash commands need provider-native handling so commands such as /status are delivered to the running backend session without being interpreted as ordinary prompt text. The backend trait keeps a default fallback while Codex resumes the existing thread with raw command stdin.
